    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Thanks for raising.\r\n\r\nWe recently updated the default log path to be under the data path if it's been specified, but it looks like the log-file-name-pattern path hasn't been updated.\r\n\r\nAs a work-around, you could specify\r\n```\r\n--log-file-name-pattern=\"/chaindata/logs/teku_%d{yyyy-MM-dd}.log\"\r\n```\r\non the command line and it should get you running again straight away.\r\n",
